Given the following program and the first line of a loop, optimize it out via loop unrolling.. The program is 
int d;
int e;
int fn1(int *h) {
  if (e)
    goto i;
  fn1(h);
  fn1(h);
  return 0xEEACFBBFL;
i:
  d = *h;
  fn1(h);
  return 0xEEACFBBFL;
}
int main() {}
.                 The target to be optimized is `if (e) goto i;` (line 3).
